Package: survblendr
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive Spline-Weighted Blending for Survival Extrapolation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Hao", "Chen", email = "hche2036@uni.sydney.edu.au", role = c("aut","cre")))
Description: Survival extrapolation by spline-weighted blending of a piecewise-exponential model fitted via INLA over the observed window and an anchored Gompertz tail.
